---
title: Login Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant LF as LoginFrame
    participant AC as AuthController
    participant DS as DataStore
    participant MF as MainFrame

    User->>LF: Enter username & password
    User->>LF: Click Login
    LF->>AC: login(username, password)
    AC->>DS: authenticate(username, password)
    DS-->>AC: User object (or null)
    alt Valid Credentials
        AC->>DS: setCurrentUser(user)
        AC-->>LF: User object
        LF->>LF: dispose()
        LF->>MF: new MainFrame(user)
        MF-->>User: Main window displayed
    else Invalid Credentials
        AC-->>LF: null
        LF-->>User: Error: "Invalid username or password"
    end
